{"tid":2053274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飛到太空才發現忘帶記憶卡，太空人持 GoPro 求救 NASA 總部","createTime":"2020-06-06T06:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T08:36:39.000Z","uid":66271,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"83b1d6ba504d1e7eb4f4240efd44aa46f669a6c7","tid":2053274,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/06/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-06-05-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.12.49.webp?png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2020%2F06%2F%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-06-05-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.12.49.webp%3Fpng&h=eb282080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNASA 在 Twitch 上公開一支剪輯 影片 ，影片中，在國際太空站（International Space tation, ISS）的太空人 Drew Feustel 發現自己的 GoPro 相機居然沒有裝記憶卡，於是緊急聯絡 NASA 總部，在一陣尷尬的沈默後，對方&hellip; 轉移話題了。<br />\n<br />\n這起事件發生在 Feustel 跟隊友 Ricky Arnold 在太空站執行維修外部冷卻系統任務的時候。為了記錄任務的過程，Feustel 打開了 GoPro，卻發現無法使用，於是他打了通電話回到地球的 NASA 總部。<br />\n<br />\n「嘿，休士頓，我有一個 GoPro 的問題？很快」Feustel 用急促的聲音詢問。<br />\n<br />\n「我們正專心聽，說吧」在地面的組員 Butch Wilmore 回應。<br />\n<br />\n「我看到沒有&hellip; 我按下按鈕了，但我看到這邊寫『no SD』，這個意思是&hellip; 錄影需要那個對嗎？如果它已經在錄影了，它應該要亮紅燈對吧？」<br />\n<br />\n地面的 Wilmore 陷入一陣沈默。<br />\n<br />\n「就我所知，如果 GoPro 在錄影， 紅燈應該要亮。」<br />\n<br />\n「但它上面寫 No SD&hellip;這是什麼意思？」<br />\n<br />\n「對，這就代表&hellip; 呃&hellip; 沒卡，我們正在確認，等一下。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0IMmHUADmw&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM0IMmHUADmw%26feature%3Demb_title&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=3fef128a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0IMmHUADmw&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"9bdcc7734dfe01ccba86ff81ede78c90b5eef8f7","tid":2053274,"uid":117893,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"發布日期：2018年5月18日"},{"pid":"6ea35a82a454147b450b947e48eefb0663aa10a3","tid":2053274,"uid":6058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"運物資上去時帶多樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5265fd40ffed06709c69e4347fb6314ccd46d78","tid":2053274,"uid":5220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"攝影師大忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d710ab04cc803c012775e0667452454972a536","tid":2053274,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"如果係香港公司實炒左人"},{"pid":"b52fb4ca11c4a9532de75b87dc29d6b5a8029aca","tid":2053274,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bdcc7734dfe01ccba86ff81ede78c90b5eef8f7","tid":2053274,"uid":117893,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"發布日期：2018年5月18日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3e13a0e5a4649c42354a9365f1286719474c9e","tid":2053274,"uid":72929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"喂，候斯頓，我地有gopro 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f42b395186b0f997488ed3696988dd55ecfb9c","tid":2053274,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"中文由translation server error 提供"},{"pid":"ba3a110b5b4ba1c34c61e510b60956787a09c18c","tid":2053274,"uid":55761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"啊，我就算怕被罵啊"},{"pid":"df464b93c67419be684f15c1c4649bc8c28147e9","tid":2053274,"uid":55761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba3a110b5b4ba1c34c61e510b60956787a09c18c","tid":2053274,"uid":55761,"like":